               <scopecontent id="aspace_48a3fc34e936daeb3e9d8a0ea3deb025">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Brochure, 28 pages, reprinted from <title>
                        <part>Yale Journal of Biology and Medicine</part>
                     </title> 13 (1941): 863-889. It contains all the speeches from the dedication and a frontispiece consisting of a photograph of the Historical Library and a transcription of George Stewart's engraved words over the fireplace.</p>
