            <c id="aspace_64fe65b7163ba2656080a5494c7b770d" level="file">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>Memorabilia collected by Madeline Stanton on the Yale Medical Library</unittitle>
                  <unitdatestructured unitdatetype="inclusive">
                     <daterange>
                        <fromdate standarddate="1939">1939</fromdate>
                        <todate standarddate="1941">1941</todate>
                     </daterange>
                  </unitdatestructured>
                  <unitdate unitdatetype="inclusive">1939-1941</unitdate>
                  <container altrender="archive letter"
                             containerid="39002010855899"
                             id="aspace_23256b30b51a6450dfb7fd5a5773a392"
                             label="Mixed Materials"
                             localtype="box">2</container>
                  <container id="aspace_d2f557f69c129669e8a0d4ef8dddc474"
                             localtype="folder"
                             parent="aspace_23256b30b51a6450dfb7fd5a5773a392">8</container>
               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_1b564e405465cb26f49abbcddfb661b9">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>These materials were pasted on backing and annotated by Madeline Stanton. In addition to pamphlets already mentioned, the folder contains a note by Wilmarth Lewis stating that the decisive date for the building of the library was September 22, 1939; two pamphlets dated May 24, 1940 and April 1941 on the progress of construction and asking "Patrons of the Yale Medical Library" for funds; an undated list of exhibits and note about a reception for the Connecticut Clinical Congress; a formal pledge of the Collection of Arnold C. Klebs dated June 16, 1941; and <title>
                        <part>Report of the Historical Library</part>
                     </title> for 1940-1941.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
            <c id="aspace_1d60a5953b797c80b298d01cfd038bc5" level="file">
