               <scopecontent id="aspace_d44e219498eaee623792e33267326e70">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>In addition to previous materials on the dedication, there is a variant program with the notice of serving tea in the Beaumont Room; a variant printing of "The Blessing of the Books"; and a page on an exhibit of selected Yale University Press books at Sterling Memorial Library presented by the Class of 1891 in memory of Harvey Cushing.</p>
